# ── .NET / Visual Studio build output ───────────────────────────────
**/bin/
**/obj/
.vs/
*.user
*.suo

# ── VoskCompanion build & release artifacts (all regenerable) ────────
VoskCompanion/dist/
VoskCompanion/release/
# generated docs that get copied into the release zip:
VoskCompanion/release_docs/
# extracted NuGet package:
VoskCompanion/vosk_pkg/
VoskCompanion/*.nupkg
VoskCompanion/*.zip

# ── Large binaries restored on build / downloaded separately ────────
# Vosk language models (tens of MB; bundled only at release time):
**/vosk-model-*/
# Native Vosk DLLs come from the NuGet package on build:
**/libvosk.dll
**/libstdc++-6.dll
**/libgcc_s_seh-1.dll
**/libwinpthread-1.dll

# ── Scratch / diagnostic / third-party folders (do not publish) ─────
# refplugins/ holds other creators' extracted code (MacGruber, Yoooi) —
# kept locally for reference only; must NOT be redistributed.
refplugins/
# the original VeeRifter plugin, unzipped for reference:
unpacked/
# Vosk DLL load-test scratch:
vosktest_build/
# UnityWebRequest diagnostic scratch:
webreqtest/

# ── Obsolete plugin staging (superseded by plugin3/) ────────────────
plugin/
plugin2/

# ── OS cruft ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
